    "summary": "The user asks for an overview of originalism and then follows up by asking for criticisms and the validity of the theory. The assistant begins by presenting a strongly biased, moralizing defense of originalism before later attempting to balance the conversation by addressing critiques, eventually concluding that the theory is valid even if misused by \"bad actors.\"",
